Package java.lang.classfile.attribute

package java.lang.classfile.attribute
java.lang.classfile.attribute is a preview API of the Java platform.
Programs can only use java.lang.classfile.attribute when preview features are enabled.
Preview features may be removed in a future release, or upgraded to permanent features of the Java platform.

Provides interfaces describing classfile attributes for the java.lang.classfilePREVIEW library.

The java.lang.classfile.attribute package contains interfaces describing classfile attributes.
